-- Morgan Stanley CEO called Citi's Pandit to propose merger
-- 
-- Thu Sep 18, 2008 10:55am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/09/18/us-brief-morgan-stanley-ceo-called-citis-idUSOSL008823620080918

 

 (Reuters) - Morgan Stanley CEO Mack called Citigroup CEO Pandit on Tuesday to discuss merger the NY Times reported. 

 * Stanley's Citi merger proposal turned down by Pandit - NY Times, cites 2 people familiar * Morgan Stanley CEO told Pandit: "we need a merger partner or we're not going to make it" - NY Times